Hi all —  The grand jury that has heard the Epstein case is set to expire in two weeks. Should we extend them in 
case the recent developments result in the unraveling of the agreement? 
Assistant U.S. Attorney 
500 S. Australian Ave, Suite 400 
West Palm Beach, FL 33401
